text: All you can ever hear, at home  --
--Turn that light out for me please?<cough>
I'll just finish what I'm doing.
I want you to brush your hair
and then go and find the library books.
Are you going to brush your hair?
Can you take these bobble in please?
They'll only get lost in mine.
Look, if you put it somewhere sensible like on the side of the mirror.
